- 12:(1,0,1), 13:(1,0.375,1), 14:(1,1,1)

Blocks:
- Block 0: left (0,1,2,3 × 9,10,11,12) - x=0→0.5
- Block 1: bottom-right (1,5,6,2 × 10,12,7,11) - x=0.5→1, y=0→0.375
- Block 2: top-right (2,6,7,3 × 11,13,14,10) - x=0.5→1, y=0.375→1

Boundary faces need updating for the new vertex positions.

